title: Bobby Renegade Mens Jean
body_html: Now something for the eco-conscious denim fan who doesn't skimp on style either. The Bobby recycled jean combines an on-trend denim look with eco-friendly material. The Recycled Renegade denim group features fabric comprised of recycled bottle yarn for the fill and the resulting jean is a piece that maintains our signature style and comfort while reducing our footprint. The yarn in contrast brown creates a unique slub texture in the fabric and becomes more intense after the garment is dyed. Surprisingly, the resulting hand is incredibly soft, not stiff like most recycled fabrics and is durable enough to withstand a considerable amount of wear.

title: Ricky Straight Super T Mens Jean
body_html: A key piece from our spring collection, this iteration of our Ricky captures the essence of our sun bleached denim series to perfection. A classic straight leg jean is the fit favorite among True Religion men and is the ideal canvas to support this edgy wash. A rigorous finishing process delivers a washed out indigo shade and is then sanded down to carry out the perfect amount of distress. A sprinkling of bleach adds a distinct touch as does the thick Super T topstitch construction in Rust. If you want your jeans to stand out rather than blend in, this is the style for you.

title: Geno Slim Straight Mens Jean
body_html: A refreshing update to winter's darker denim is our new sunbleached jeans for spring. The Geno in Light Antelope wash is a key piece from this collection as it captures the lightened up look in a modern way. Our signature slim straight Geno fit is perfectly tailored yet still has enough room for added comfort and carries out a polished look effortlessly. Premium denim sourced from iconic American mills is used to create this classic five pocket jean. A considerable amount of acid washing and dye treatments results in a washed out denim look that is on-trend for this season. Each piece has been thoroughly treated by hand in order to carry out a one-of-a-kind appearance.

title: Indigo Pattern Western Mens Shirt
body_html: A classic chambray shirt gets a western revival with a traditional print. The vertical pattern is featured on pre-washed and distressed fabric to ensure a natural vintage appearance while the slim fit was made to suit the modern man. Snap buttons, a western yoke and smile pockets are the finishing touches that make this piece authentic.

title: Shoulder Beaded Womens Tank
body_html: Embellished accents decorate the neckline and shoulders of this sleek tank for a boho inspired piece to pair with your favorite distressed denim. The effortless fabric and easy silhouette is just too comfy not to wear all year round. The shiny metallic details add an ideal amount of sparkle underneath a jacket or blazer so you don't have to wait until summer time to break it out. Also available in Cream and Black.

title: Solid Single Pocket Mens Shirt
body_html: We're returning back to basics this season and paying homage to time-honored classics like the staple button down. This iteration follows a minimal motif highlighted by a single chest pocket and branded hardware. In basic white, it's a style that's perfect for dressing up and as such, belongs in every man's closet.

title: Erin Rolled Crop Relaxed Denim Womens Overall
body_html: Spring is in the air and that means a wide array of lighter looks to look forward to. In addition to more muted palettes, a lighter and more relaxed attitude towards fashion (see: playful approaches), highlight a number of trends this season. Take this denim patchwork overall, for example. The boyfriend fit carries out a relaxed style that's reminiscint of the favorite rompers of our childhood. It's a denim look that's fun, refreshing and one-of-a-kind especially with the expertly sourced and restored denim squares featured on the front.

title: True Flatlock Mens Tee
body_html: Get a rugged and iconic look with a renovated version of our Ricky. A bright rope stitch detail in a rust colored shade highlights this classic five pocket design for a distinct denim style that can never be recreated. The dark wash features thoroughly sanded areas for pronounced highs and lows and contrasts boldy with the updated stitching.

title: Stars Womens Tank
body_html: This high low tank highlights our passion for vintage Americana fashion. A distressed flag emblazoned on the back is the original creation of our in-house design team and pays homage to our roots. The effortless silhouette is slightly more modern than the art and features an elongated tail on the back composed of the softest material imaginable. It's the perfect piece to sport once the weather warms up and festival season hits.

title: Chrissy Super Skinny Womens Jean
body_html: Spring is in the air and one of our key pieces of the collection is this gorgeous garden party of a jean. Printed denim continues to be a hallmark of each season and couldn't look more seasonally appropriate than with a colorful floral pattern on a subdued forest green skinny. A shorter 29" inseam ensures a smooth fit with minimal stacking and creates the perfect pant to pair with sandals because once the sun comes out, the toes start to make appearances too!

title: Rattle Indigo Mens Tee
body_html: Adding to our array of hand illustrated tees is the Rattle Indigo shirt in Indigo Blue. This classic crew neck features an original rattlesnake logo created by our in-house design team. The idea was to bring our western roots and passion for denim into a single tee that we envision being worn with our premium jeans. The material is equally as impressive as the artwork with a vintage hand that feels almost like a second skin.

title: Rocco Slim Selvedge Mens Jean
body_html: Selvedge denim tightly woven on old shuttle looms is constructed into a modern slim style for an updated version of a classic look. The iconic identifier of authentic selvedge denim, the red and white seam or "self edge", is visible when the jean is worn with a folded cuff and is repeated on the coin pocket. A handcrafted wash carries out whiskers and creases for a well aged apperance and will continue to get better with each wear. We recommend minimal washing to develop characteristics in the denim that all your own.

title: Solid Single Pocket Mens Shirt
body_html: We're returning back to basics this season and paying homage to time-honored classics like the staple button down. This iteration follows a minimal motif highlighted by a single chest pocket and branded hardware. In basic black, it's a style that's perfect for dressing up and as such, belongs in every man's closet.

title: Ricky Straight Renegade Jean
body_html: Authentic, made in America denim is truly something special and our Renegade Group encapsulates the look and feel of vintage jeans right down to the details. The Ricky in Desert Drought is a prime example of the Renegade Collection with its rugged appeal that will no doubt stand the test of time. In order to carry out a perfectly aged and classic Americana appearance, our premium denim has been painstakingly distressed by hand. Our signature straight leg silhouette, the Ricky, captures the essence of a time honored fit with a traditional five pocket design and accents of color in the stitching.

title: Ricky Straight Big Qt Mens Jean
body_html: This seasonal jean is a fine denim specimen that showcases our sunbleached and sandblasted series of denim perfectly. After heavy stone and enzyme washing, we accomplished a unique crinkled, faded and distressed appearance to this straight leg jean. Muted, multicolored thread weaves through this classic five pocket design in our signature Big QT style for a look that's irresistible to the True Religion denim devotee.

title: Bjml Mystic Water Clean
body_html: Embrace your inner spirit warrior with clothing that embodies your wild side. A destroyed and distressed skinny jean highlighted by our new Mystic Water wash mirrors the desert sky encountered by our adventurous True Religion woman. The muted palette and soft hand is achieved by a handcrafted wash on lightweight 9.25 oz stretch denim and appears well worn like a beloved pair of pants.

title: Direction Womens Tee
body_html: Our in-house design team revamped our logo and returned it to a more classic style in this time-honored tee. The fit is more modern to maintain a certain level of feminine appeal and the hand is as soft as skin to mimic the feel of a vintage shirt. It's perfect for the no-fuss kind of gal who wants something simple to wear with her everyday denim. It's so easy and effortless that possessing only one just doesn't seem practical.

title: Joey Low Rise Denim Cut Off Womens Short
body_html: What polar vortex? There's no trace of winter here in LA. In fact, spring is starting to warm up nicely and could even warrant wearing a thigh high short in this weather. If it's sunny where you are or if you can't fathom wearing anything skin baring but want to stock up on staples a season early, then the Joey jean shorts are for you. It features flattering back flap pockets, a sunbleached wash and a cheeky hemline with frayed edges so you can show off those stems and give your gams some breathing room after its long hibernation.

title: Single Pocket Plaid Twill Mens Shirt
body_html: A classic chambray shirt gets a western revival with a traditional print. The vertical pattern is featured on pre-washed and distressed fabric to ensure a natural vintage appearance while the slim fit was made to suit the modern man. Snap buttons, a western yoke and smile pockets are the finishing touches that make this piece authentic.

body_html: A classic crew neck tee in army green is highlighted by an eagle emblem on the front for a nod to time-honored, American military style. In order to encapsulate a signature vintage effect, a thorough handcrafted wash was applied. An added bonus is the superbly soft hand that comes with our natural distress process.

title: True Flatlock Mens Tee
body_html: Get a rugged and iconic look with a renovated version of our Ricky. title: Womens Long Cardigan
body_html: According to this week's forecast, it's safe to pack away winter's beloved parka. Luckily, in it's place is a lightweight knit cardigan that's perfect for throwing on over your favorite jeans and button down or if it's warmer where you are (we Angelenos are basking in 75 degree temps during this "winter" week), a pair of shorts and a tee.
